# Project Stack

- React 19 + Vite (no TypeScript)
- Plain CSS with CSS custom properties for design tokens -- no Tailwind
- Design tokens live in `src/tokens.css` (colors, spacing, typography, corners)
- Components are `.jsx` files in `src/`
- Inter font loaded via Google Fonts in `index.html`

# Conventions

- Use CSS custom properties from `src/tokens.css` instead of hardcoded values
- When adding new design tokens, add them to `src/tokens.css` first
- Keep component styles in `src/App.css` (or colocated CSS files as the project grows)
- Assets go in `src/assets/`
